yourself, Alex.

41:01.568 --> 41:03.576
From where I'm sitting,
you did everything right.

41:03.648 --> 41:06.615
And I would be the first one
to tell you if you didn't.

41:15.999 --> 41:17.309
Thank you.

41:22.431 --> 41:23.992
We have an indictment?

41:24.063 --> 41:25.078
Yes.

41:26.016 --> 41:27.477
Good work, Alex.

41:27.551 --> 41:28.566
